|author=John Percy
|title=Birmingham City 2 Blackpool 2 (2-3 on agg): match report
|work=the Telegraph
|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/competitions/championship/9254026/Birmingham-City-2-Blackpool-2-2-3-on-agg-match-report.html
